OL,3,CSir Jeffrey Donaldson takes to stand
OL,4,Cin sex abuse trial
OL,6,FFormer DUP leader Sir Jeffrey
OL,7,FDonaldson has said he is "crystal
OL,8,Fclear" that an allegation he raped an
OL,9,Falleged victim when she was a child is
OL,10,F"simply not true".
OL,12,FDonaldson also told his sexual
OL,13,Foffences trial that an allegation that
OL,14,Fhe had touched the same woman's
OL,15,Fbreasts was "just unbelievable".
OL,17,FThe ex-MP, 63, has pleaded not guilty
OL,18,Fto 18 alleged offences.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUpD@FO]rD@AOUrD@QO]wD@MOUwD@_O]
