OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1781190689
OL,3,CSir Jeffrey Donaldson takes to stand
OL,4,Cin sex abuse trial
OL,6,FThe charges include one count of rape
OL,7,Fand allegations of indecent assault
OL,8,Fand gross indecency, and span a time
OL,9,Fperiod between 1985 and 2008 involving
OL,10,Ftwo alleged victims.
OL,12,FComplainant A and B have both given
OL,13,Fevidence at the trial. Both women
OL,14,Fallege they were abused as children.
OL,16,FEleanor Donaldson, 60, denies several
OL,17,Fcharges of aiding and abetting her
OL,18,Fhusband's alleged offending.
OL,20,FShe is facing a trial of the facts on
OL,21,Fmental health grounds.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/12
