PN,44305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1781190689
OL,3,CSir Jeffrey Donaldson takes to stand
OL,4,Cin sex abuse trial
OL,6,FThe court has previously heard
OL,7,Fevidence about a letter Donaldson
OL,8,Fwrote to Complainant A in June 2020,
OL,9,Fwhere he had told of his "regret" over
OL,10,Fthe "hurt, pain and distress I have
OL,11,Fcaused".
OL,13,FThe defence has previously told the
OL,14,Fcourt the letter does not relate to
OL,15,Fany alleged abuse, but is about
OL,16,Fanother matter.
OL,18,FDonaldson read extracts of the letter
OL,19,Fto the court.
OL,26,@qD@ZOUqD@aO]rD@EOUsD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1781190689
OL,3,CSir Jeffrey Donaldson takes to stand
OL,4,Cin sex abuse trial
OL,6,FMr Vaughan asked him if the letter
OL,7,Freferred to incidents of abuse.
OL,9,FDonaldson said "Absolutely not." He
OL,10,Fadded: "This is not the reason why
OL,11,Fthis letter was written."
OL,13,FThe barrister turned to the
OL,14,Fallegations made by Complainant B, who
OL,15,Fclaims she was raped by Donaldson.
OL,17,FDonaldson told the court: "It just
OL,18,Fdidn't happen, I am absolutely crystal
OL,19,Fclear about that."
OL,26,@qD@POUqD@`O]rD@HOUsD@YO]yD@[OU{D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1781190689
OL,3,CSir Jeffrey Donaldson takes to stand
OL,4,Cin sex abuse trial
OL,6,F"It is not something I would ever have
OL,7,Fdone, it is just simply not true."
OL,9,FMr Vaughan turned to another incident
OL,10,Fwhere it is alleged Donaldson had
OL,11,Flifted the girl's top and touched her
OL,12,Fbreasts.
OL,14,FDonaldson said he did remember an
OL,15,Foccasion being alone with the girl,
OL,16,Fbut said they had just been talking.
OL,18,FHe said he got up and left when he
OL,19,Fheard his wife, Eleanor, call his name.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/12
