PN,44308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1781190689
OL,3,CSir Jeffrey Donaldson takes to stand
OL,4,Cin sex abuse trial
OL,6,FMr Vaughan asked if there had been any
OL,7,Finappropriate behaviour.
OL,9,FHe said: "Absolutely none whatsoever.
OL,10,FThere was nothing I would have done
OL,11,Fthat could be misconstrued."
OL,13,FHe said the idea was "just
OL,14,Funbelievable".
OL,16,FDonaldson also rejected any suggestion
OL,17,Fthat his wife had witnessed the abuse
OL,18,Fbut did not intervene.
OL,26,@qD@JOUsD@\O]uD@VOUvD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/12
