PN,44309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1781190689
OL,3,CSir Jeffrey Donaldson takes to stand
OL,4,Cin sex abuse trial
OL,6,FHe said: "She would have been very
OL,7,Fangry, she would have intervened
OL,8,Fimmediately."
OL,10,FHe added: "I am absolutely clear,
OL,11,Fthere is no situation where that
OL,12,Fhappened.
OL,14,F"I would not have been doing that. It
OL,15,Fis just unbelievable."
OL,17,FAsked about other allegations of
OL,18,Finappropriately touching the same
OL,19,Falleged victim, he said: "Absolutely
OL,20,Fnot."
OL,26,@nD@JOUpD@MO]rD@KOUvD@AOUwD@VO]{D@ZOU|D@
