OL,3,CSir Jeffrey Donaldson takes to stand
OL,4,Cin sex abuse trial
OL,6,FThe court has previously heard that
OL,7,FDonaldson had met with Complainant B
OL,8,Fin the 1990s after she attended the
OL,9,FChristian Family Centre in Armoy.
OL,11,FDonaldson said at the meeting he had
OL,12,Fsaid he was sorry if Complainant B had
OL,13,Ffelt "uncomfortable".
OL,15,FMr Vaughan asked if any allegation of
OL,16,Fsexual abuse was put to him at the
OL,17,Fmeeting.
OL,19,FHe said: "No, not ever, those
OL,20,Fallegations had never been put to me."
OL,26,@uD@FOUuD@TO]{D@JOU|D@fO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/12
